#: src/features/user/login.tsx:828
msgid "You won't be able to sign in with {0} anymore. Make sure you still have another way to log in."
msgstr "Cha bhi e comasach dhut soidhnigeadh a-steach le {0} tuilleadh. Dèan cinnteach gu bheil dòigh eile agad fhathast airson log-a-steach."

#: ../../../lib/web/src/components/restore-banner.tsx:91
msgid "Your account was moved here from {source}. Until you delete it there, messages and notifications may reach both servers, some of your content keeps being served from the old server, and followers may take a few minutes to find you here."
msgstr "Chaidh do chunntas a ghluasad an seo à {source}. Gus an sguab thu às e an sin, faodaidh teachdaireachdan agus brathan ruighinn air an dà fhrithealaiche, bidh cuid den susbaint agad ga frithealadh bhon t-seann fhrithealaiche, agus faodaidh luchd-leantainn beagan mhionaidean a ghabhail gus do lorg an seo."

#: src/features/user/close-account.tsx:126
msgid "Your account will be permanently deleted on {purgeDate}. You've been signed out. To cancel, sign in again before then."
msgstr "Thèid an cunntas agad a sguabadh às gu buan air {purgeDate}. Chaidh do chlàradh a-mach. Gus sgur dheth, clàraich a-steach a-rithist roimhe sin."

#: src/features/user/close-account.tsx:94
msgid "Your account will be scheduled for deletion and you'll be signed out. You can cancel any time before the deletion date by logging back in. Download your data first if you want to keep a copy."
msgstr "Thèid do chunntas a chlàradh airson a sguabadh às agus thèid do chlàradh a-mach. 'S urrainn dhut a chur dheth uair sam bith ron cheann-latha sguabaidh às le bhith a' clàradh a-steach a-rithist. Luchdaich a-nuas do dhàta an toiseach ma tha thu airson lethbhreac a chumail."

#: src/features/user/replication.tsx:219
msgid "Your account's data on this server will be permanently deleted and you'll be signed out here. Your account stays on your other servers, and you can re-add this one later."
msgstr "Thèid dàta a' chunntais agad air an fhrithealaiche seo a sguabadh às gu buan agus thèid do chlàradh a-mach an seo. Fanaidh an cunntas agad air na frithealaichean eile agad, agus 's urrainn dhut am fear seo a chur ris a-rithist nas fhaide air adhart."

